original: Egberg, Thor August Sigfrid, kyr-koiherde, Skirö, f. 6/5/02 i Voxtorp, Kalmar 1., av kontr ’.prosten August E. o. Anna Deurell. G. 38 m. Maria Haglund. Barn: Karin f. 39, Britta 42, Marianne 46. — Stud:ex. i Lund 22, fil. kand. där 26, teol. kand. o. prakt. teol. prov 31, prästv. f. Växjö stift 32. Tjg. s. past:adj. i Odensjö o. Långasjö, s. v. pastor i Skirö o. Al-seda samt s. v. kommin. i S. Solberga, kyrkoh. i Skirö sed. 39. Hobby: målning.
translated: Egberg, Thor August Sigfrid, church captain, Skirö, born May 6th, 1902 in Voxtorp, Kalmar county, son of district provost August E. and Anna Deurell. Married in 1938 to Maria Haglund. Children: Karin b. 1939, Britta b. 1942, Marianne b. 1946. Education: graduated from Lund in 1922, bachelor's degree in philosophy there in 1926, bachelor's degree in theology and practical theology examination in 1931, ordained as a priest for the diocese of Växjö in 1932. Served as a pastor's assistant in Odensjö and Långasjö, vicar in Skirö and Al-seda, and assistant minister in S. Solberga before becoming the parish priest in Skirö in 1939. Hobby: painting.
